{"tid":1276064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（G20）特朗普：曾與習近平談及港修例引發示威","createTime":"2019-07-02T01:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T05:21:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":277,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"1aaddb83dccc2a8e7c514c2a679765d2203fda86","tid":1276064,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:13:21.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，曾與國家主席習近平在二十國集團(G20)峰會期間，談及香港修訂《逃犯條例》引發的示威，他並對發生衝突感到難過。<br />\n<br />\n他回應示威者闖入香港立法會時表示，相信香港人追求民主，大部分人追求民主，但有政府不要民主。特朗普強調，示威關乎民主。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人則稱，促請各方避免使用暴力。香港成功在於法治以及尊重基本權利，包括自由表達及和平集會。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國會眾議院議長佩洛西在社交網站表示，香港人近期抗議修訂《逃犯條例》的行動令舉世獲得啟發。她說，G20國家或全球都不應忽視港人的勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2178710/特朗普%3A曾與習近平談及港修例引發示威\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2178710%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%253A%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%AB%87%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=8f654bef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2178710/特朗普%3A曾與習近平談及港修例引發示威</a>"},{"pid":"a8f1ea50cef8f090c10800236ed20eccf8409a52","tid":1276064,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1459ff3cf994e501fcb7c578d9577057a438d173","tid":1276064,"uid":56063,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:16:48.000Z","msg":"翻譯唔敢譯俾敗北知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者失腳大喝一聲叫人唔好譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8151d533f35f1b60f1b764e3f842c02b4217f3e2","tid":1276064,"uid":194398,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9f95ef9bd9fb7085a08b5e1eb91d038dd46520a","tid":12760